snippet.title: Lou's Lagoon - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
See plane customization, exploration, and more in this new Lou's Lagoon trailer for the upcoming adventure game. In Lou's Lagoon, fly, jump, and glide into a vibrant island adventure!
Your Uncle Lou has disappeared and left his seaplane delivery service in your hands, so now it’s up to you to keep the business afloat – and discover what happened to him! Lou's Lagoon will be available on PC.
